    <text>
        <body>
            <div style="handwritten" type="letter" xml:id="d.1">
                <head type="title">Daniel Mauch to Miklós Oláh (Leuven, 26 May 1536)</head>
                <floatingText type="regesta">
                    <body>
                        <p xml:id="reg.p.1">If he was not on his way out, he would thank him longer
                            for his praise, but because he is leaving soon, he thanks him now. </p>
                    </body>
                </floatingText>
                <pb/>
                <p xml:id="p.1">Daniel <del corresp="Olahus">Mauch</del><add corresp="Olahus"
                        type="corr">Mauchius</add> Nicolao Olao salutem. </p>
                <p xml:id="p.2">Reverende et Magnifice Domine, Patrone mihi Colendissime. Nisi
                    festinaret auriga et serius mihi Reverendissimae Dominationis Vestrae
                        litterae<note type="critic" xml:id="note.1">We do not know this
                        letter.</note> redditae essent, multis verbis gratias agerem, quod tantum
                    meo nomine facere dignata est, sed quia perendie
                        <placeName>Bruxellae</placeName> futurus sum, Magnificentiae Vestrae
                    praesens gratias agam, et interim semperque habebo. Bene valeat Reverendissima
                    Dominatio Vestra, cui me humillime commendo. </p>
                <p xml:id="p.3">Ex <placeName>Lovanio</placeName> XXVI. Maii 1536.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
